Summary (Exam-Ready)
As of 2026, blockchain adoption remains modest among the general population (about 3.9 % of people worldwide), but enterprise adoption is very high (~90 %), with many industries using blockchain for payments, supply chains, data security, and asset tokenization. The global blockchain market is also expanding rapidly, with strong projected growth and increasing use by institutions and businesses.

